<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PhD Admissions Abroad | Manya Education</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/Phd_Adroad.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/Home.css">
</head>
<body>

    <!--  Header -->

    <%- include('partials/header') %> 

    <!-- page-container   -->
    <div class="page-container">
        <section class="hero-section">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>PhD Admissions Abroad</h1>
                <div class="breadcrumb">
                    <a href="/">Home</a>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
                    <a href="/admissions">Admissions</a>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
                    <span>PhD Admissions</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="main-content">
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="content-left">
                    <div class="content-section">
                        <p>What is PhD? Obtaining a Doctor of Philosophy (PhD) is a large investment of time and resources that can provide a person with valuable knowledge, experience in conducting research, and promotion in the respective field of study. People pursue PhDs to advance knowledge in their areas of study, satisfy the spirit, and get exclusive job opportunities.</p>
                        
                        <div class="highlight-stats">
                            <p>Worldwide, about two percent of the population has a Doctor of Philosophy degree which shows how rare this level of education is as well as the recognition that comes with it.</p>
                            <p>The average earnings of PhD holders in the USA are $98,000 per annum while for holders of master's degrees is $76,000 per annum.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>Why Study a PhD abroad?</h2>
                        <div class="benefits-grid">
                            <div class="benefit-item">
                                <h3>Advanced Research Facilities</h3>
                                <p>Universities of the world are well endowed with quality laboratories and research instrumentation that offer students a platform to undertake quality and relevant research.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="benefit-item">
                                <h3>Global Networking and Collaboration</h3>
                                <p>Availing a study abroad opportunity enables Indian students to work with other students, teachers, and professionals internationally.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="benefit-item">
                                <h3>Exposure to Diverse Perspectives</h3>
                                <p>Studying and living in different countries help students to gain experience in different cultures and approaches to problem-solving.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="benefit-item">
                                <h3>Enhanced Career Opportunities</h3>
                                <p>Obtaining a PhD degree from any recognized University of international reputation increases one's chances of getting employment.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>Popular trending PhD programs</h2>
                        <table class="programs-table">
                            <tr>
                                <th>PhD Program</th>
                                <th>Key Features</th>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>PhD in Artificial Intelligence</td>
                                <td>Focuses on machine learning, neural networks, natural language processing, and robotics, preparing graduates for roles in academia, tech companies, and research labs.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>PhD in Data Science</td>
                                <td>Emphasizes big data analytics, statistical modeling, and computational techniques, equipping students to tackle data-driven challenges.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>PhD in Biotechnology</td>
                                <td>Covers genetic engineering, pharmaceuticals, and bioinformatics, preparing students for careers in research, healthcare, and industrial applications.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>PhD in Cybersecurity</td>
                                <td>Focuses on information security, cryptography, and risk management, preparing students to lead cybersecurity teams.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>PhD in Psychology</td>
                                <td>Specializes in clinical psychology, cognitive neuroscience, or organizational behavior, equipping graduates for roles in academia.</td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="content-right">
                    <form class="enquiry-form" id="enquiryForm" action="/submit-phd-enquiry" method="POST">
                        <h3>Planning to study abroad?</h3>
                        <p>Get free 1-on-1 counselling with our experts</p>
            
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" required>
                            <label for="firstName">First Name</label>
                        </div>
            
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="text" id="lastName" name="lastName" required>
                            <label for="lastName">Last Name</label>
                        </div>
            
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                            <label for="email">Email</label>
                        </div>
            
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="tel" id="mobile" name="mobile" pattern="[0-9]{10}" required>
                            <label for="mobile">Mobile No. (10 digits)</label>
                        </div>
            
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <select id="program" name="program" required>
                                <option value="">Select Program</option>
                                <option value="TOEFL">TOEFL</option>
                                <option value="IELTS">IELTS</option>
                                <option value="GRE">GRE</option>
                            </select>
                            <label for="program">Select Program</label>
                        </div>
            
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <select id="mode" name="mode" required>
                                <option value="">Select Mode</option>
                                <option value="Classroom">Classroom Coaching</option>
                                <option value="Online">Online Coaching</option>
                            </select>
                            <label for="mode">Select Mode</label>
                        </div>
            
                        
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <select id="city" name="city" required>
                                <option value="">Select City</option>
                                <option value="Noida">Noida</option>
                                <option value="Delhi">Delhi</option>
                                <option value="Gurgaon">Gurgaon</option>
                            </select>
                            <label for="city">Select City</label>
                        </div>
            
                        <div class="checkbox-group">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="authorize" name="authorize" required>
                            <label for="authorize">I authorize Manya - The Princeton Review to contact me even if my number is registered with DND to assist with my enquiry and get regular updates through SMS/Whatsapp.</label>
                        </div>
            
                        <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Submit</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('partials/footer')%>
    </div>

    <script src="../js/Home.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/Phd_Abroad.js"></script>

</body>
</html>